2x\" /></a></span> <span typeof=\"mw:File\"><span><img src=\"/images/thumb/d/d6/%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%99%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%9E%D7%97%D7%95%D7%93%D7%A9_5.svg/16px-%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%99%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%9E%D7%97%D7%95%D7%93%D7%A9_5.svg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"16\" height=\"11\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d6/%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%99%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%9E%D7%97%D7%95%D7%93%D7%A9_5.svg/24px-%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%99%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%9E%D7%97%D7%95%D7%93%D7%A9_5.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d6/%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%99%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%9E%D7%97%D7%95%D7%93%D7%A9_5.svg/32px-%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%99%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%9E%D7%97%D7%95%D7%93%D7%A9_5.svg.png 2x\" /></span></span></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chabad.info/special/1099030/\">\"רואים וחיים כל הזמן עם הרבי\"</a> ראיון לקראת <a href=\"/index.php/%D7%92%27_%D7%AA%D7%9E%D7%95%D7%96\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"ג&#39; תמוז\">ג' תמוז</a> <a href=\"/index.php/%D7%AA%D7%A9%D7%A4%22%D7%93\" title=\"תשפ&quot;ד\">תשפ\"ד</a> <span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/index.php/%D7%97%D7%91%22%D7%93_%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95\" title=\"חב&quot;ד אינפו\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/27px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"27\" height=\"9\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/41px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/54px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg 2x\" /></a></span></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.hageula.com/sichat_hageula/Life/26566.htm\"><b>\"צריך להגיע ל-770 כדי להבין\"</b></a> ראיון שהעניק לגליון <a href=\"/index.php/%D7%A9%D7%99%D7%97%D7%AA_%D7%94%D7%92%D7%90%D7%95%D7%9C%D7%94\" title=\"שיחת הגאולה\">שיחת הגאולה</a> לאחר ביקורו 